snippet: Winston met with officials at the league’s headquarters, according to a spokesman, which is unusual for a player who has yet to be drafted.
abstract: NFL Roundup; former Florida State quarterback Jameis Winston reportedly meets with NFL commissioner Roger Goodell and other league officials in New York less than two months before the draft.
lead_paragraph: Winston met with officials at the league’s headquarters, according to a spokesman, which is unusual for a player who has yet to be drafted.

headline.main: Jameis Winston Meets With Roger Goodell and Other N.F.L. Officials
